{"label": "droite", "transcript": [{"text": "Monsieur le pr\u00e9sident.", "start": 1.316, "duration": 1.167}, {"text": "Alors voil\u00e0, nous y sommes.", "start": 2.483, "duration": 0.967}, {"text": "Il y a trois ans,", "start": 3.45, "duration": 0.8}, {"text": "tout le monde se r\u00e9jouissait", "start": 4.25, "duration": 0.933}, {"text": "de voir pleuvoir sur l'Europe", "start": 5.183, "duration": 1.133}, {"text": "de l'argent magique,", "start": 6.316, "duration": 0.75}, {"text": "avec cet emprunt qui surgissait.", "start": 7.066, "duration": 1.934}, {"text": "Et aujourd'hui,", "start": 9.0, "duration": 0.533}, {"text": "cet emprunt", "start": 9.533, "duration": 0.383}, {"text": "dont personne ne savait", "start": 9.916, "duration": 0.75}, {"text": "comment il serait rembours\u00e9,", "start": 10.666, "duration": 1.567}, {"text": "nous sommes face au co\u00fbt", "start": 12.233, "duration": 0.817}, {"text": "qu'il repr\u00e9sente.", "start": 13.05, "duration": 0.616}, {"text": "Ce co\u00fbt", "start": 13.666, "duration": 0.634}, {"text": "devait \u00eatre de 15 milliards\u00a0d'euros,", "start": 14.3, "duration": 1.416}, {"text": "l'\u00e9quivalent de tous nos", "start": 15.716, "duration": 1.05}, {"text": "programmes spatiaux", "start": 16.766, "duration": 0.75}, {"text": "en Europe sur sept ans.", "start": 17.516, "duration": 1.734}, {"text": "Eh bien, aujourd'hui,", "start": 19.25, "duration": 1.166}, {"text": "il a certainement explos\u00e9,", "start": 20.416, "duration": 1.5}, {"text": "m\u00eame si nous ne le savons pas,", "start": 21.916, "duration": 1.417}, {"text": "puisque la Commission,", "start": 23.333, "duration": 1.05}, {"text": "monsieur le Commissaire,", "start": 24.383, "duration": 0.833}, {"text": "nos coll\u00e8gues le disaient", "start": 25.216, "duration": 0.734}, {"text": "tout \u00e0 l'heure,", "start": 25.95, "duration": 0.766}, {"text": "ne publie pas aujourd'hui", "start": 26.716, "duration": 1.15}, {"text": "le co\u00fbt actualis\u00e9 de cet emprunt", "start": 27.866, "duration": 1.834}, {"text": "dans le contexte de l'inflation.", "start": 29.7, "duration": 1.733}, {"text": "Chers coll\u00e8gues,", "start": 31.433, "duration": 0.683}, {"text": "nous parlions il y a quelques ann\u00e9es", "start": 32.116, "duration": 1.5}, {"text": "d'argent frais.", "start": 33.616, "duration": 0.75}, {"text": "Aujourd'hui nous parlons d'imp\u00f4ts.", "start": 34.366, "duration": 1.484}, {"text": "Et tout le monde parle ici", "start": 35.85, "duration": 1.2}, {"text": "de nouvelles taxes.", "start": 37.05, "duration": 0.683}, {"text": "Car ces nouvelles ressources propres,", "start": 37.733, "duration": 1.767}, {"text": "c'est bien s\u00fbr de fiscalit\u00e9", "start": 39.5, "duration": 1.65}, {"text": "qu'il s'agit.", "start": 41.15, "duration": 0.933}, {"text": "Je crois qu'il est temps de rappeler", "start": 42.083, "duration": 0.9}, {"text": "deux choses :", "start": 42.983, "duration": 0.4}, {"text": "que nous devons", "start": 43.383, "duration": 0.867}, {"text": "aux citoyens de nos pays", "start": 44.25, "duration": 1.016}, {"text": "la transparence sur la politique", "start": 45.266, "duration": 1.584}, {"text": "budg\u00e9taire de l'Union europ\u00e9enne", "start": 46.85, "duration": 1.166}, {"text": "- cette transparence,", "start": 48.016, "duration": 0.684}, {"text": "elle est cruciale,", "start": 48.7, "duration": 1.333}, {"text": "et que nous devons nous souvenir,", "start": 50.033, "duration": 1.5}, {"text": "\u00e0 la fin,", "start": 51.533, "duration": 0.783}, {"text": "que tout imp\u00f4t est toujours, toujours,", "start": 52.316, "duration": 2.534}, {"text": "le r\u00e9sultat du travail", "start": 54.916, "duration": 1.6}, {"text": "de ceux qui nous ont fait confiance", "start": 56.516, "duration": 1.884}, {"text": "en nous donnant mandat", "start": 58.4, "duration": 0.75}, {"text": "pour les repr\u00e9senter ici.", "start": 59.15, "duration": 1.466}, {"text": "Il n'y a pas d'imp\u00f4t", "start": 60.616, "duration": 0.85}, {"text": "qui puisse \u00eatre lev\u00e9,", "start": 61.466, "duration": 1.1}, {"text": "comme s'il \u00e9tait une solution magique", "start": 62.566, "duration": 1.634}, {"text": "aux probl\u00e8mes que nous n'aurons pas", "start": 64.2, "duration": 0.916}, {"text": "su r\u00e9soudre.", "start": 65.116, "duration": 0.784}, {"text": "C'est la condition", "start": 65.9, "duration": 0.633}, {"text": "pour que nous soyons vraiment", "start": 66.533, "duration": 0.867}, {"text": "\u00e0 la hauteur", "start": 67.4, "duration": 0.75}, {"text": "des g\u00e9n\u00e9rations qui viennent.", "start": 68.15, "duration": 0.983}]}